Troubleshooting
API Connection Refused

Ensure Flask server is running: ps aux | grep api_server.py
Check port 5000 is not in use: netstat -tuln | grep 5000
Restart server if needed
Authentication Failures

Verify token is exactly: dev-token-12345
Check Authorization header format: Bearer <token>
Ensure token file has correct permissions
Import Errors

Activate virtual environment: source venv/bin/activate
Reinstall packages: pip install requests click tabulate flask flask-httpauth
JSON Parsing Errors

Verify API returns valid JSON: curl http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/health
Check response status codes before parsing
